msgstr "ID ng Gawain"

#: app/htmx/setup_step_routes.py:363
msgid "Building Count"
msgstr "Bilang ng Gusali"

#: app/htmx/setup_step_routes.py:397
msgid ""
"No task boundaries found. Please split the project into tasks first using"
" the \"Split AOI\" button above."
msgstr ""
"Walang nahanap na hangganan ng gawain. Hatiin muna ang proyekto sa mga "
"gawain gamit ang button na \"Split AOI\" sa itaas."

#: app/htmx/setup_step_routes.py:453
#, python-format
msgid ""
"✓ AOI split successfully! Generated %(task_count)s task areas using "
"%(algorithm)s."
msgstr ""
"✓ Matagumpay na nahati ang AOI! Nakabuo ng %(task_count)s task area gamit"
" ang %(algorithm)s."

#: app/htmx/setup_step_routes.py:460
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Previewing %(task_count)s task boundaries%(data_extract_info)s. Review "
"the results below. If satisfied, click \"Accept Task Choices\" to save. "
"Otherwise, adjust parameters above and click \"Split Again\" to "
"regenerate."
msgstr ""
"Ipinapakita ang preview ng %(task_count)s hangganan ng "
"gawain%(data_extract_info)s. Suriin ang mga resulta sa ibaba. Kung ayos "
"na, i-click ang \"Accept Task Choices\" para i-save. Kung hindi, ayusin "
"ang mga parameter sa itaas at i-click ang \"Split Again\" para muling "
"buuin."

#: app/htmx/setup_step_routes.py:547 app/htmx/setup_step_routes.py:680
msgid "Data Extract"
msgstr "Nakuha na Data"

#: app/htmx/setup_step_routes.py:560
#, python-format
msgid "OSM data downloaded successfully! Found %(feature_count)s features."
msgstr ""
"Matagumpay na na-download ang OSM data! Nakakita ng %(feature_count)s "
"feature."

#: app/htmx/setup_step_routes.py:563
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Previewing %(feature_count)s features on map. Review the data below. If "
"satisfied, click \"Accept Data Extract\" to save. Otherwise, try "
"downloading again with different parameters."
msgstr ""
"Ipinapakita ang preview ng %(feature_count)s feature sa mapa. Suriin ang "
"data sa ibaba. Kung ayos na, i-click ang \"Accept Data Extract\" para "
"i-save. Kung hindi, subukang mag-download muli gamit ang ibang mga "
"parameter."

